data.title: Ulverstone Cemetery
data.text:
Transcribed by Darryel McLean

from photographs provided by Marylin and Steve Jones

I do not wish to offend anyone by listing this information on the website, as the work is done with the best intentions of providing vital information to family historians. All the information shown here is on public display at the respective cemeteries.

We have made every effort to be as accurate as possible. If you find any errors, please CLICK HERE

If you would like to provide information on family or leave a query on the Oz Burials Message Board, please click on the link below.

Post a Message on the Oz Burials Message Board - Registration is free.

Photographs are freely available CLICK HERE please advise cemetery name.

If you wish to make a donation to help defray the costs of operating the site, thank you.

We do not charge for the photos that are made available.

Donations are accepted through PayPal Secure payment
